      "beast_baseline": "thanks that makes sense. i think i'll add the delete line now. but just to be sure, is there anything else that could cause this to happen in a bigger system? like, are there any other \"hidden\" ways memory just disappears or gets stuck like this without it being an obvious missing delete?",
